node.text:
#ApexThatP320

PC: @firearmpatriot
・・・
This is the Apex Tactical Trigger Kit for the  Sig P320 and X Series. It greatly reduces uptake, overtravel and reset on my X5 Legion. No change in the 4lbs and 3oz trigger pull which is what was advertised.  However, you should have a reduction of pull weight on the P320 models. I love dealing with Apex. You can always expect their products to do what they say. #apextactical #apextrigger #wdtr #allhailtheflatty #sigp320x5 #sigp320x5legion #sigsauerp320x5legion
